  ¡§Chhin-ai3 e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2, Pa-pa cha2-khi2 m7-chiah8.¡¨ Ma2-kek-liat8 koaN2-kin2 chau2 loh8--lai5 kong2: ¡§Ma-ma, chhin-ai3 e5 Ma-ma, Pa-pa kong2 cha2-khi2 m7-chiah8.¡¨ ¡§Ma2-kek-liat8, li2 boe7 hiau2-tit. Li2 tioh8 chhiaN2 Pa-pa loh8-lai5!¡¨ Ma2-kek-liat8 chiu7 koh chiuN7 lau5-teng2, i e5 ma-ma ia7 toa3 i khi2-lai5. Hit lang5 thiaN-kiN3 i e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 e5 kha-pou7 siaN, chiu7 eng7 chin jin5-chu5 e5 siaN kong2: ¡§Goa2 e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 ah, lai5 goa2 chia.¡¨ I e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 ia7 kiaN ia7 kian3-siau3, ban7-ban7 kiaN5 kau3 i e5 bin7-cheng5, i chiu7 pho7 i e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2, che7 ti7 i ka-ki7 e5 kha-thau5-u teng2. I ka7 i e5 cha-bou2-kiaN2 chim-chhui3 liau2-au7, chiu7 chhut-siaN thi5-khau3. I e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 khia7 ti7 lau5-thui-thau5, bok8-beng5 ki5-biau7 . I koh tui3 i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kong2, ¡§Chhin-ai3 e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 ah, chhiaN2 lai5.¡¨ Tui3 an2-ni i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 ia7 lai5 che7 ti7 i to3-peng5 e5 kha-thau5-u teng2. I e5 siang-chhiu2 pho7 i e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kap cha-bou2-kiaN2. I e5 hu7-jin5-lang5 kap cha-bou2-kiaN2 koe3 khi3 siong5 siu7 koe3 i chiong2-chiong2 e5 phaiN2 khoan2-thai7, na7 si7 kin-a2-jit8 i pho7 in, ka7 in chim-chhui3, koh aN3-thau5 chhut-siaN toa7 thi5-khau3, cheng5-chong7 kin2-tiuN sim7-chi3 lau5-teng2 ui7-tioh8 an2-ni tin2-tang7. 
